00019 IMUFilter::IMUFilter(const ColumnVector& sys_noise_mu, const SymmetricMatrix& sys_noise_cov, const ColumnVector& measurement_noise_mu, const SymmetricMatrix& measurement_noise_cov):

00041         A(constants::RY_STATE(), constants::RY_DOT_STATE()) = 1;
00042         A(constants::RZ_STATE(), constants::RZ_DOT_STATE()) = 1;
00043 
00044         //Build Input Matrix
00045         Matrix B(12,3);
00046         B = 0;

00049         B(constants::Z_DOT_STATE(), constants::Z_DOT_DOT_INPUT()) = 1;

00052         this->AB_[0]   = A;

00066 
00067         //Build Measurement PDF/Model
00068         Gaussian measurement_uncertainty(measurement_noise_mu, measurement_noise_cov);
00069         this->mes_pdf_   = new LinearAnalyticConditionalGaussian(H, measurement_uncertainty);

00084 bool IMUFilter::init(const ColumnVector& initial_state, const SymmetricMatrix& initial_covar)
00085 {
00086         //Check to make sure sizes match up
00087         if(initial_state.size() == constants::STATE_SIZE() && initial_covar.size1()==constants::STATE_SIZE())
00088         {
00089                 this->prior_       = new Gaussian(initial_state, initial_covar);
00090                 this->filter_      = new ExtendedKalmanFilter(this->prior_);
00091                 this->filter_init_ = true;
00092                 return true;
00093         }
00094         else
00095         {
00096                 ROS_ERROR("Cannot Initialize IMU Filter with State/Covar size %d/%d, Expecting Size %d/%d", initial_state.size(), initial_covar.size1(), constants::STATE_SIZE(), constants::STATE_SIZE());
00097                 return false;
00098         }
00099 }
